{"tid":814034,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"尼泊爾東南部不明疾病致3死逾400人染病","createTime":"2018-09-11T02:11:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-11T03:08:51.000Z","uid":77196,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"6e6b1c6f6aa2a2123d667fea4e86d55569a7b3ad","tid":814034,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T02:11:04.000Z","msg":"尼泊爾東南部堪昌拉布地區，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>過去15天出現不明疾病，至今已有3名男童死亡</strong></span>，400多人染病。<br />\n<br />\n當地傳媒引述衞生部門負責人稱，3名男童在醫院不治，發病時都有高燒症狀。染病的400多人，則有高燒、肌肉痙攣、咳嗽、關節疼痛和頭痛等症狀。<br />\n<br />\n尼泊爾流行病與疾病控制部門表示，已經分析病人的樣本，初步認為他們是患上叢林斑疹傷寒或某種流感，但最終結果仍需要進一步分析。"},{"pid":"48308141220f507ecf03c9ae269901185e4a75e7","tid":814034,"uid":186608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T02:12:10.000Z","msg":"沙士 2.0 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1907749a01bacb1b0211b95f6957e97bedaa5a8","tid":814034,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T02:18:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfcc6dc2ca8e4940a604ac9635c7db4d84b9a118","tid":814034,"uid":202412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T03:05:58.000Z","msg":"瘟疫公司<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc77d97561f96966b3be5775676de5448371d9ca","tid":814034,"uid":66686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dfcc6dc2ca8e4940a604ac9635c7db4d84b9a118","tid":814034,"uid":202412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T03:05:58.000Z","msg":"瘟疫公司<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T03:07:05.000Z","msg":"咁大殺傷力死唔到幾多人<img src=\"/asse